<i>adverb</i>: 환히 [환ː히], 화려히 [화려히], 찬란히 [찰ː란히], 명랑히 [명낭히] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>환히 [환ː히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. brightly; radiantly</dd><br>
<dd>빛이 비치어 맑고 밝게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being very clear and bright as light shines.</dd><br>
<dd>2. openly; clearly</dd><br>
<dd>앞이 탁 트여 넓고 시원스럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of something imparting a feeling of not being confined, because it has an open view.</dd><br>
<dd>3. clearly; obviously</dd><br>
<dd>무슨 일이 되어 가는 사정이나 속내가 분명하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of the progress or intention of a certain event being clear.</dd><br>
<dd>4. attractively; finely; neatly</dd><br>
<dd>얼굴이 깔끔하게 잘생겨 보기에 좋게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of having a pleasing, neat, and attractive appearance.</dd><br>
<dd>5. brightly; beamingly; radiantly</dd><br>
<dd>표정이나 성격이 명랑하고 밝게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of one's face or personality being bright and cheerful.</dd><br>
<dt>화려히 [화려히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. colorfully; splendidly; radiantly</dd><br>
<dd>곱고 아름다우며 환하게 빛나 보기에 좋게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state of looking good, being beautiful, bright, and shiny.</dd><br>
<dd>2. luxuriously; extravagantly; flashily</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이나 생활 등이 보통 사람들이 누리기 어려울 만큼 대단하거나 사치스럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of one's job or life being too luxurious and fancy to be enjoyed by average people.</dd><br>
<dt>찬란히 [찰ː란히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. brightly; radiantly</dd><br>
<dd>강한 빛이 번쩍이거나 수많은 불빛이 빛나는 상태로. 또는 그 빛이 매우 밝고 환하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of a bright light flashing or many lights shining, or in the manner of the lights being very bright.</dd><br>
<dd>2. splendidly</dd><br>
<dd>빛깔이나 모양 등이 매우 화려하거나 아름답게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of the color, appearance, etc., of something being very magnificent or beautiful.</dd><br>
<dd>3. gloriously</dd><br>
<dd>일이나 이상 등이 매우 좋고 훌륭하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of a matter, ideal, etc., being very good and grand.</dd><br>
<dt>명랑히 [명낭히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. radiantly</dd><br>
<dd>흐린 데 없이 밝고 환하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Shiningly and brightly without cloudiness.</dd><br>
<dd>2. merrily</dd><br>
<dd>유쾌하고 활발하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a cheerful and outgoing manner.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>